*  Linux system programming
*
**/

Assignment : Write a program which accept file name and number of bytes from user and read that number of bytes from file.

Description :
Will use open system call for openning the specified file, and will use the read system call to read the specific byte of data from the file.

NOTE:
Assuming parameter sequence as follows
1. file name
2. Number of bytes to read

Will print the fetched information from the file.